      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Incident",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "[unclear] 1208-1[unclear]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "[unclear] August 1947",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "MEMORANDUM FOR THE OFFICER IN CHARGE:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "1. On 5 August 1947, this agent interviewed [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "[REDACTED] the assistant operations officer in the 416th AAF BU,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Building 68, Hamilton Field, California, regarding flying objects in the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "air. [REDACTED] stated in substance: He is an [REDACTED] in",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "the 416th Training Unit. On 29 July at 1450, [REDACTED] and a student,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "[REDACTED] Berkeley, California, landed",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "and parked an AT-6 near the hangar, building 68 of the 416th AAF BU.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Walking from the aircraft toward reserve operations, and looking westward",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "just over the hangar, [REDACTED] saw a P-80 flying southward toward",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Oakland. Above this P-80, at approximately 8,000 to 10,000 feet in alti-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "tude, [REDACTED] saw two flying objects traveling the same direction",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "as the P-80. He, [REDACTED] judged the solid, white, somewhat shiny objects",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "were approximately 15 to 25 feet in diameter. [REDACTED] stated that he",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "didn't call them discs due to the publicity these objects have been given",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "but in shape they were circular, like a ball on the bottom, but not com-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "pletely round, and [REDACTED] specifically stated that these objects were not",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "airplanes.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "2. The first flying object was traveling straight and level, whereas",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "the second was close behind the first, same altitude, only it seemed to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "be going from left to right and right to left, more or less like a guard",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "in an aircraft formation. [REDACTED] further stated that the speed",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "of these two objects made a P-80 look as if it was motionless in the air.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "3. The sky was clear, consequently [REDACTED] watched",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "the two objects until they disappeared in flight, supposedly over Oakland,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "headed toward the ocean.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "4. Due to the noise of the P-80, no sound of any kind could be heard from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "these flying objects.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "5. These objects did not leave any vapor, smoke, or any visible trails",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "along their flight path.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "6. [REDACTED] informed this agent he had never told anyone about",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "these flying objects, fearing that people would think he was crazy.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "AGENT'S NOTES: [REDACTED] showed extreme sincerity throughout the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "interview, answering all questions with caution and assurance.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "JAMES A. NELSON, Specl Agt, CIC 4AF",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
